snippet: After missing the previous two months with a back injury, Venus Williams lost to Kirsten Flipkens, 0-6, 6-4, 6-2, at the Rogers Cup in Toronto in just under two hours.
abstract: Belgian Kirsten Flipkens defeats Venus Williams at Rogers Cup; match is Williams's first following two month recovery from back injury.
lead_paragraph: After missing the previous two months with a back injury, Venus Williams lost to Kirsten Flipkens, 0-6, 6-4, 6-2, at the Rogers Cup in Toronto in just under two hours.

headline.main: Venus Williams, Still Not at 100 Percent, Loses in Return
